---
title: Classic Cheeseburgers with Sweet Relish and Seasoned Wedges
description: Is there anything better than an ooey-gooey cheeseburger with all the fixings?! We think not! And making it yourself is that much more satisfying. The side of seasoned wedges turns this meal into the perfect takeout-fakeout!
